    {
      "type": "text", "id": "support_text",
      "x": 920, "y": 680, "width": 820, "height": 100,
      "text": "📦 /dikw-context    — manage session memory, cross-level context carry-over\n📁 /dikw-workspace  — scaffold project dirs, manage artifacts, standardize paths\n\nPRINCIPLE: skill-first development. The SKILL.md prompt is the source of truth;\nmake each skill work in Claude Code, THEN deploy to cloud agents.",
